        <div class="about-content">
            <p class="about-text">
                Ignitia is an AI-based platform for wildfire risk prediction and fire spread simulation. 
                It uses satellite imagery, climate data, and machine learning to forecast fire-prone zones 
                and simulate spread in real time across a 30m radius.
            </p>
            <p class="about-text">
                Our advanced algorithms analyze environmental factors including vegetation indices, 
                topographical data, weather conditions, and historical fire patterns to provide 
